quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  20,106,"Nígbà náà, Ó máa fi wọ́n sílẹ̀ ni pẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀ gban̄sasa."
  20,107,"O ò sì níí rí ọ̀gbun tàbí gelemọ kan nínú rẹ̀."
  20,108,"Ní ọjọ́ yẹn, àwọn ènìyàn yóò tẹ̀lé olùpèpè náà, kò níí sí yíyà kúrò lẹ́yìn rẹ̀. Àwọn ohùn yó sì palọ́lọ́ fún Àjọkẹ́-ayé. Nítorí náà, o ò níí gbọ́ ohùn kan bí kò ṣe gìrìgìrì ẹsẹ̀."
  21,82,"Nínú àwọn aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n, àwọn tó ń wa kùsà òkun tún wà fún un. Wọ́n tún ń ṣe iṣẹ́ mìíràn yàtọ̀ sí ìyẹn. Àwa sì ń jẹ́ Olùṣọ́ fún wọn."
  21,83,"(Ẹ rántí Ànábì) ’Ayyūb, nígbà tí ó pe Olúwa rẹ̀ pé: “Dájúdájú ọwọ́ ìnira ti kàn mí. Ìwọ sì ni Aláàánú jùlọ nínú àwọn aláàánú.”"
  21,84,"A sì jẹ́pè rẹ̀. A mú gbogbo ìnira rẹ̀ kúrò fún un. A tún fún un ní àwọn ẹbí rẹ̀ (padà) àti irú wọn pẹ̀lú wọn; (ó jẹ́) ìkẹ́ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Wa àti ìrántí fún àwọn olùjọ́sìn (fún Wa)."
  22,58,"Àwọn tí wọ́n gbé ìlú wọn jù sílẹ̀ nítorí ẹ̀sìn Allāhu, lẹ́yìn náà, tí wọ́n pa wọ́n tàbí tí wọ́n kú; dájúdájú Allāhu yóò pèsè fún wọn ní ìpèsè tó dára. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Ó mà l’óore jùlọ nínú àwọn olùpèsè.{1}.",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah as-Sọ̄ffāt; 37:125.]
  22,59,"Dájúdájú (Allāhu) yóò fi wọ́n sínú àyè kan tí wọn yóò yọ́nú sí. Dájúdájú Allāhu mà ni Onímọ̀, Aláfaradà."
  22,60,"Ìyẹn (nìyẹn). Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì gbẹ̀san irú ìyà tí wọ́n fi jẹ ẹ́, lẹ́yìn náà tí wọ́n bá tún ṣàbòsí sí i, dájúdájú Allāhu yóò ṣàrànṣe fún un. Dájúdájú Allāhu mà ni Alámòjúúkúrò, Aláforíjìn."
  23,34,"Tí ẹ bá fi lè tẹ̀lé abara kan bí irú yín, dájúdájú ẹ mà ti di ẹni òfò nìyẹn."
  23,35,"Ṣé ó ń ṣe àdéhùn fún yín pé nígbà tí ẹ bá kú, tí ẹ sì di erùpẹ̀ àti egungun tán, dájúdájú wọn yóò mu yín jáde (ní alààyè)?"
  23,36,"Ohun tí Wọ́n ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fún yín (yìí) jìnnà tefétefé (sí òdodo)."
  24,16,"Nígbà tí ẹ gbọ́ ọ, kí ni kò jẹ́ kí ẹ sọ pé: “Kì í ṣe ẹ̀tọ́ fún wa pé kí á sọ èyí. Mímọ́ ni fún Ọ (Allāhu)! Èyí ni ìparọ́-mọ́ni tó tóbi.”"
  24,17,"Allāhu ń ṣe wáàsí fún yín pé kí ẹ má ṣe padà síbi irú rẹ̀ mọ́ láéláé tí ẹ bá jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."
  24,18,"Allāhu ń ṣàlàyé àwọn āyah náà fún yín. Allāhu sì ni Onímọ̀, Ọlọ́gbọ́n."